1991 started project with Sun Microsystems
	idea was cross-platform programming, wrote Java
	2010 oracle bought Sun, and java

Differences between Java and C++
	built in garbage collection (deleting pointers)
	Uses references instead of pointers
	Data types are always the same size
	specific boolean datatype, and constructs are made to use it
	classes dynamically linked at runtime, no seperate link step
	java is hybrid compiled/interpreted language
	...
